 FY 2026 – FY 2027 Funding Rationale:
 Funding was not requested in FY 2026 and FY 2027 due to delays in MILCON project timelines, which shifted POE implementation to the right. Prior-year resources will be executed in alignment with updated
 facility availability and project schedules.




